OL,5,G0010 999: On the Front Line
OL,6,     FThe paramedics rush to a man who's
OL,7,     Freportedly not breathing, but
OL,8,     Fthere's a surprise when they
OL,9,     Farrive. And the team help a
OL,10,     Ftwo-year-old who's having a
OL,11,     Fseizure.
